microservice AppUser, Profile, FileUser with ms_user

microservice Province, District, Ward, Address, Station, Route, Vehicle, SeatMap, Floor, Seat, Schedule, ScheduleTimeSlot, ScheduleOccasion, Trip, Staff, Driver, Attendant, SeatLock, FileRoute with ms_route

